DarkMouse::

She stepped out of the chamber and stretched her arms. She felt much 
better and quite in the good mood. She walked out of the chamber room 
and towards the bridge again where her station was at.  She walked 
passed the mess hall and decided to see the parts of the ship she 
hadn't seen yet.  Letting her nose guide her, so to speak, she went 
down towards the brig. She wondered who might be locked up down here. 
And if so, how long? Spare parts were always high in demand no matter 
who's side you were on. Besides, maximal parts could be used for so 
many different things.
